{"tid":1876661,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"買咗湖北製造嘅紙巾","createTime":"2020-02-12T14:05:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-12T14:09:37.000Z","uid":303059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"39666d3fcb51c1c785a3db89e07950de4c5dd9f8","tid":1876661,"uid":303059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T14:05:03.000Z","msg":"利申非膠post<br />\n<br />\n家父返屋企嗰時見佢買咗兩條紙巾，<br />\n心諗佢喺邊度買到咁好野。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點知一睇原來係湖北製造嘅垃圾大陸野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，問佢佢就話喺佢做野附近啲細鋪買到嘅，買嗰時又無留意到喺湖北造<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n究竟風險大唔大?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n宜家就用兩個膠袋入住嗰兩條紙，諗住聽日dum咗佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fozen_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有無巴打可以教下我應該點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n係屋企就無紙巾用，老豆先見到就心急買咗<br />\n巴打屌細力啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a30b86933a2040a81234e9249e6ea5d0e8c4c5d","tid":1876661,"uid":5883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T14:05:37.000Z","msg":"下世小心啲啦"},{"pid":"b8a5f1e1b263992c36fa4e064161a66cf9239919","tid":1876661,"uid":160734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T14:09:37.000Z","msg":"蒸完晾乾咪得囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}